name: Anonymous Leader #1 : Big Lub
description: #1 of the series: "Anonymous Leader", focused on different depictions of Satoshi Nakamoto. The series explores relationships between bitcoin and political movements of the past, revisiting many of the issues bitcoin was created to solve. Vector art exported in 6250 x 9376 pixels.
